title: 9. Real Talk: Letting Go Of The Ego And Looking At The Bigger Picture
itunes:title: 9. Real Talk: Letting Go Of The Ego And Looking At The Bigger Picture
description: Some people’s egos are so big, that they are willing to risk a good thing to satisfy their need to always be right. It’s time to wake up and realize what really matters.
